{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_51_01",
  "title": "小美山愛 1話 父の力になりたくて",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁぁ……どうしよう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haaa… what should I do…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "愛、どうしたの？　ため息なんてついて\nこころにまたイタズラされた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ what's wrong? Sighing like that…\nDid Kokoro play another prank on you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、イタズラはされていないんですが……『ミラクル\n☆アイドルバースデー！』のお仕事について悩んでて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it’s not a prank… I’m worried about the\n“Miracle ☆ Idol Birthday!” job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……！　愛ちゃんにも、お話が来たんだね\nでも、悩みって……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow…! You got an offer too‚ Ai-chan!\nBut… what’s your worry?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.3747785568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "誕生日に合わせて、なんでも願いを叶えてくれる\nっていう企画なんでしょ？　そんなに悩むことある？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s that project where they grant you any wish\non your birthday‚ right? What’s there to worry about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "お話をもらえたのは嬉しいんですが、集中出来なくて\n……実は、私の実家が一世一代のピンチなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m happy to have received the offer‚ but I can’t focus.\n…Actually‚ my family’s business is facing a once-in-a-lifetime crisis.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0333344777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ！？　愛ちゃんの実家って\nラーメン屋さんだったよね？　何があったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? Your family’s business…\nis a ramen shop‚ right? What happened?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4999970754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "最近、実家の近所にラーメンの有名チェーン店が出来て\nうちからお客さんが離れちゃったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Recently‚ a famous ramen chain opened near my house‚\nand customers have been leaving our shop.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.4333304088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "実家の売り上げは下がるばかりで……「なんとかする」\nとは言ってるけど、お父さんも元気がないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our sales are dropping… My dad kept saying\n“I'll do something”‚ but he looked depressed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.3999970754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "私もせっかく誕生日企画の話をもらったのに、そっちが\n気になっちゃって。アンケートも手につかなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got this great offer for a birthday project‚ but I’m so worried about that.\nSo‚ I can’t even concentrate on the questionnaire…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9938737455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "それは心配だね。なんとか出来ればいいんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… That’s worrying. I hope there’s something we can do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.5333293915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "こころに相談したら、そのチェーン店を\n爆破しようって言われちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I asked Kokoro for advice‚ she said\nlet's blow up the chain store.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1999960582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "こころらしいね。まぁ現実的に考えると\n爆薬は用意出来ないから、襲撃くらいになりそうだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds like Kokoro. Well‚ realistically speaking‚\nIt is impossible to get explosives‚ so it would be just the raid.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1333339692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　ダ、ダメですよそんなの\nせめて犯人だとバレないように、事故を装わないと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? N-no way! That's not good!\nWe have to make it look like an accident so we don’t get caught!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1666586559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "この間観たホラー映画で、小さなことが連鎖して\n最終的に大きな事故に繋がるっていうシーンが――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the horror movie I watched the other day‚ a series of small events\nultimately led to a major accident――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2999940237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "解決方法が過激過ぎますよ！？　あと襲撃は葵さんの\n冗談ですから！　千紗さんも真に受けないで下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your solution is too extreme! And raiding the place was\njust Aoi-san’s joke! Chisa-san‚ don’t take it seriously!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.0999919892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、冗談なんだ。良かったぁ……\nどういう装置を作ろうか一瞬考えちゃったよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ it was a joke. That’s a relief…\nI was just thinking about what kind of apparatus to build…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5666586559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "最終手段として準備しておくのは\n悪くなさそうだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wouldn’t be a bad idea to have it ready\nas a last resort‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5999919892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "と、とにかく！　大変な時期なので、いっそお仕事を\nお休みして、実家に帰ろうかと思ってるんです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-anyway! It’s a tough time‚ so I’m thinking of\ntaking a break and going back home…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3666586559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "仕事を休む……ね。愛、そこは逆じゃないかな\n特に今回の誕生日企画は、絶対に受けた方がいいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Taking a break… hey. Ai‚ wouldn’t that be counterproductive?\nEspecially‚ you should definitely take this birthday project offer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.1000062307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、実家のことが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But my family’s business…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7000062307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "実家のことが心配なんでしょ？　だから、その誕生日\n企画の中で、実家の手伝いをさせてもらえばいいんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re worried about your family‚ right? Then‚ for that birthday project‚\nyou can ask to help out at your family’s business.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.6666718801,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "なんでもお願いを叶えてくれる企画なんだから\n愛が今、やりたいことをお願いしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a project where they grant you any wish‚\nso Ai‚ ask for what you want to do right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.9305567198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "それ、凄くいいアイデアですね……！\nそれなら雑誌にお店のことが載って、宣伝にもなるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a really good idea…!\nThen your family’s shop will be featured in a magazine‚ and it’ll be good publicity!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.4000052135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "私の誕生日企画が、実家の助けに……\nそっか……そっか……！　その手がありました……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My birthday project could help my family…\nI see… I see…! There was a way…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.6333385468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！　早速、父に相談してみます！\nちょっと頑固ですけど、喜んで許可してくれるかと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you! I’ll talk to my dad right away!\nHe’s a little stubborn‚ but I think he’ll be happy to allow it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.5000052135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A Few Days Later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.4666718801,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1433.3332061000021,
          "startTime": 197.9000050862
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "葵さん、千紗さん、どうしましょう！？\nお父さんから許可をもらえませんでした～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi-san‚ Chisa-san‚ what should I do!?\nI couldn't get the permission from my dad~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.033339564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "えぇー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehh!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.4999919892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに、さっきの誕生日企画の打ち合わせで\n大丈夫です！　って大見得を切ってしまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Furthermore… in the birthday project meeting earlier‚\nI confidently boasted like‚ it will be okay!…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.6000031789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどね。許可を取らないうちに\n話がとんとん拍子に進んじゃってる、ってことか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. So things are moving along smoothly\nwithout his permission‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.8666698456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "しかも何度父に頼んでも、考えさせてほしいの\n一点張りで……当日に間に合えばいいんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And no matter how many times I ask my dad‚ he just says\nhe’ll think about it… I hope we can make it in time for the day…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.3000041962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、ダメでもいろいろ方法はあると思う\nそれよりその企画、僕も参加していい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I think there are ways to work around it even if he doesn’t agree.\nMore importantly‚ can I participate in that project?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.233343633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "葵さんが、ですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi-san…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.8333324433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "うん。一緒にお店を手伝うよ\n可愛い後輩が困ってるんだ。それくらいはしないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I’ll help out at your shop.\nMy cute junior is in trouble. I have to do at least that much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.3000102997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "私も、愛ちゃんの力になりたいな\n何かお手伝い出来ることはある？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also want to help you out‚ Ai-chan.\nIs there anything I can do to help?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.033343633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "葵さん、千紗さん……！　ありがとうございます！\nでは、お二人には当日、呼び込みと接客をお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi-san‚ Chisa-san…! Thank you!\nOkay‚ then I’ll ask you two‚ for attracting customers and serving on the day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 261.1999818166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。それでもお客さんが来なかったら\nいつでも襲撃出来るように、準備をしておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. But if no one comes‚\nI’ll be ready to raid the chain store at any time.",
        "id": ""
