      "text": "はい、千紗。鉄パイプ\n莉央のだけど、借りていこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here‚ Chisa. An iron pipe.\nIt’s Rio’s‚ but let’s borrow it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 276.6999451955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "ふぇ？　あ、これ、ゾンビ映画でよく見ますね\n本物はこんな感じなんだぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Ah‚ I’ve seen this a lot in zombie movies.\nSo this is what the real thing feels like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.0332785289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
