      "text": "襲撃の準備はいりませんよ！？\n千紗さんも変に感動しないで下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We don’t need to prepare for a raid!?\nChisa-san‚ don’t be weirdly impressed!",
        "id": ""
