      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "……「お父さんへ。同じ事務所の、葵さんと千紗さんも\nお店を手伝ってくれることになりました」",
      "translations": {
