      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai021.m4a",
      "text": "「自分でなんとかしたい気持ちは分かるけど、私も\nお父さんの力になりたい。頼ってほしいな」……っと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“I know you want to do it yourself‚ but\nI also want to be your strength. I want you to rely on me.” …There.",
